src:
RBK-sjefen avslører drapstrusler
06 Nov 2019, 16:53 by Christian Skare Stendal
RBKs organisasjonssjef Trond Alstad sier at flere enkeltpersoner i Rosenborg har mottatt drapstrusler.
Det forteller han i Adresseavisens podkast «Rasmus&Saga» denne uken.
text:
The RBK commander reveals murder threats
06 Nov 2019, 16:53 by Christian Skare Stendal
RBK's head of organization Trond Alstad says that several individuals in Rosenborg have received murder threats.
He says that in Adresseavisen's podcast "Rasmus & Saga" this week.
